Mzansi Magic’s Mnakwethu: Happily Ever After? fans were impressed by Qondanisa’s second wife, Samantha, who on this week’s episode stuck to her guns and dealt with her husband accordingly. Qondanisa has two wives, MaMchunu and KaMazibuko, also known as Samantha. This week, Qondanisa called his wives to a meeting with an intention to confess that he is planning to take a third wife, with or without their blessings. This after MaMchunu had found out that he had blocked them (the wives) on his cellphone in order for him to post his girlfriend who happens to have a child with him. When Qondanisa shared the news, the wives did not take it well, leading to Samantha, who is pregnant, dropping a bombshell. She told Qondanisa that she is not certain who the father of the child is. The revelation rubbed Qondanisa the wrong way. Tension settled and emotions ran high as Qondanisa ordered Samantha to summon Diaz (Samantha’s male friend) to the meeting. Qondanisa has always suspected Diaz of having an affair with Samantha. Diaz obliged and rocked up at the meeting, but denied the allegations. Samantha then revealed that she had made a mistake and had a one-night stand with Diaz’s cousin. The revelation left Qondanisa angry, confused and speechless, to the delight of many fans of the popular reality show. This is how fans reacted to Samantha’s bombshell:        For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.